description: This Chainlink VRF common Anurak purrs with a rating of 24, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 24, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, 8 for East, 8 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20241-88893-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [24 Votes, Common]
